                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860830-31-off171 t17860830-31-cd172"></join> last, five ounces weight of enamel, value 1 l. 5 s. two ounces and an half of other enamel, value 15 s. two ounces of other, value 15 s. two ounces of other, value 12 s. two ounces of other, value 10 s. one ounce of other, value 5 s. a china globe, value 10 s.
