                     <interp inst="t17860830-31-verdict175" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               humbly recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
